# Image reading workflow
# Batch creation, mammogram review, opinions

Start /reading
Scope /dashboard /reading
Exclude /prototype-admin /api /assets /settings /clinics /participants /reports
Tags reading core
Limit pages 80
Limit depth 12

--- Setup ---

Use setup.clinician

--- Map ---

# Static pages
Visit /dashboard
Visit /reading

# Interactive flow: click through batch creation and opinions
Click "a[href*='/create-batch']"
Snapshot
Click "button:has-text('Normal')"
Wait 1000
Snapshot
Click "button:has-text('Technical recall')"
Wait 1000
Snapshot

# Form interaction: select radio, click button
Click "input[value='keep']"
Click "button:has-text('Continue')"
Wait 1000
Snapshot

# Checkbox + dropdown interaction
Check "input[value='RCC']"
Wait 500
Select "#technicalRecall-RCC-reason" "Image obscured"
Click "button:has-text('Continue')"
Wait 1000
Snapshot
Click "button:has-text('Confirm and save')"
Wait 1000
Snapshot
Click ".nhsuk-forward-link"
Wait 1000
Snapshot

# More static pages
Visit /reading/create-custom-batch
Visit /reading/clinics/mine
Visit /reading/clinics/all
Visit /reading/history/mine
Visit /reading/history/all
Visit /reading/priors
Visit /reading/priors/not-requested
Visit /reading/priors/requested
Visit /reading/priors/resolved
